strings:
<voice_0x010010D2><se_high>Red: How many times 'ave I told ya to clear off, eh?
But you still keep comin' back, don't you,
you doughnut!
<voice_0x010010D3><se_high>Red: Ever since you've 'ooked up wiv those blokes yer travellin' wiv, you've changed.
<voice_0x010010D5><se_high>Red: Just look at yer face! You've lost yer oomph! There's not an 'int of the old Yangus left in ya!
